Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.68,0:24:15.54,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}务必觅得
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.62,0:24:20.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}微眠之约
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.18,0:24:41.67,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}萌生此等惬意  实乃徒增彷徨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.00,0:24:52.64,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}予君之意  君不知乎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.37,0:24:58.51,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}察其目光  未萦他意
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.83,0:25:03.80,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur7.5}宛如待友  毫无二致
